I haven't made this exact recipe, but i've made a similar one. An alternative way to get the lemon flavor in is to put a few large pieces of lemon rind (careful to cut off the pith) in the cream as it's simmering. Then you remove them. It gives a subtle lemon flavor without the zest, and without thinning the sauce with the lemon juice.

